> 
> My game glitches out when I load the command pod with this in-game. The screen goes dark, and all the planets have disappeared.

I forgot to put an "@" to the MM config file, very sorry about that. I'll make sure this wont happen again next time.

Here is how to make it work properly :

open MM\_IXS\_IVA.cfg file inside .\GameData\WarpShip\Spaces\ with notepad,

then put an @ to each line just like below :

@PART[wsIXSCommandModule]

{

 @INTERNAL

 {

 @name = IXS\_Command\_Int

 }

}

